<p>When the <code>minutes</code> is 8, it goes like this: &quot;Is it <code>true</code> that 8 is less than 7? No. Next, is it <code>true</code> that 8 is equal to 7? No. Next, is it <code>true</code> that 8 is equal to 8? Yes, it is, so print out the line <code>It's boiling!</code>&quot;.</p>

